Text: "I went to banaras(varansi) and it was the best trip of my life, i got to know\
  \ so many things, thr architecture of villa, the story of king(raja\u2019s) it was\
  \ quite interesting, and the most important part was the ganga aarti, it was jus\
  \ wow, special thing was food iam jus loving it specially \u201Cpaanipuri\u201D\
  \ from kashi viswanath bhandar amazing paanipuri i ever had in my life and that\
  \ too the behaviour of that puchkawala bhaiya, great personality The way he was\
  \ treating his customers that was very pure hearted! I went there 3times and enjoyed\
  \ the best paanipuri ever! The journey was too good! I miss it"
